This is basically a scaled down port of King Of Fighters XIII. For a mobile game, its not bad, but don't expect this to be a perfect replica of its console counterpart. It is however much better than the G-Gee version, which has 20 characters, where as this one has 34, plus more gameplay modes. Played this on my Nexus 4 running Android 4.3, and has worked flawlessly so far. My device is unlocked but not rooted. If you are a fighting game fan, you may want to give this a shot. KOF fans should definitely get this. Would give this a perfect score if it had gamepad support, especially the ones made by Moga.
